snippet.title: Johnny Depp! Be happy. Amber Heard! Fly away.
snippet.description:
Full text of my protestation you can read below:
(caution! It is russian English)

"Amber Heard! Fly away."

I can have an accent
& bad voise  & vote
But I wanna send you
What I once time wrote…


You must be poor,
You must be fool,
You must be evil - so, you need smth... tool?

Brainless heart. Or
Contrariwise -
You can forget of the things that so nice.....

Get you hands out
From our dude!
You must invent
Smth interesting new.

Stupid young bitch
Wanna be rich –
My private opinion
I’m sending to you
 an Amber a Heard…

  From Crimea with love.


Johhny Depp!  Happy Birthday, by the way
& my respect to Vanessa Paradis.
